<div id="review_1653552099" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1653552099" />
    <a title="Douglas Wilson" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1258773-douglas-wilson"><img alt="Douglas Wilson" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442450821p2/1258773.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1653552099?book_show_action=true">May 30, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Douglas Wilson" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Douglas Wilson" href="/user/show/1258773-douglas-wilson">Douglas Wilson</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1258773-douglas-wilson?shelf=culture-studies">culture-studies</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1258773-douglas-wilson?shelf=humor">humor</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1653552099" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17971065963065580051">Three stars because the quality of the stories was all over the place. Some rated much higher, others lower. The stories were, in turn, bawdy, folksy, funny, and shrewd. But one of the things that struck me was how lightly adultery was treated in the 14th century. The natural man was alive and kicking, with a thin whitewash of Christian sentiment to make it seem okay.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


